Thanks for taking a look guys!

@lukasmasuch Definitely and I could help with debugging/testing, but I don't feel comfortable sharing our nginx config publicly. Would you mind if I share it by e-mail?

@sfc-gh-nbellante Having a `server.websocketPingInterval `configuration would be handy, thanks! But wouldn't Tornado > 6.4.2 still disallow me to set that Streamlit setting to anything lower than tornado's `ping_timeout` (30s)? So wouldn't that be the same problem packed differently?

I guess my title was inaccurate and should be "Frequent websocket connection drops with a high ping_interval setting"
